>{{cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2021/01/06/twitter-locks-trump-out-of-his-account-for-at-least-12-hours/|title=Twitter locks Trump out of his account for at least 12 hours|publisher=Tech Crunch|date=2021-01-07|accessdate=2021-04-27|archive-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608185002/https://techcrunch.com/2021/01/06/twitter-locks-trump-out-of-his-account-for-at-least-12-hours/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2021年1月7日，特朗普发布了最后两则贴文就是他不会出席新总统的就职典礼及75,000,000个美国人是爱国者。但Twitter发表声明表示，永久冻结特朗普的账号<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-55597840|title=Twitter 'permanently suspends' Trump's account|publisher=BBC.com|date=2021-01-09|accessdate=2021-04-27|archive-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608185025/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-55597840|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。其后，他宣布成立自己的平台，但该推文已经删掉。

