* 2008年8月：Twitter停止了对英国用户的免费短消息服务<ref>{{Cite_web |accessdate=2009-06-14 |url=http://blog.twitter.com/2008/08/changes-for-some-sms-usersgood-and-bad.html |title=Changes for Some SMS Users—Good and Bad News |publisher=Twitter (blog) |date=2008-08-13 |archive-date=2009-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090618143403/http://blog.twitter.com/2008/08/changes-for-some-sms-usersgood-and-bad.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，随后的五个月中，一个通过[[XMPP|XMPP]]机器人的即时信息服务也处于不可用状态<ref>{{Cite_web |url=http://getsatisfaction.com/twitter/topics/twitter_im_down_may_23rd_may24th |date=2008-05-23 |first=Jack |last=Dorsey |authorlink=Jack Dorsey |title=Twitter IM Down May 23–24 |publisher=[[Get_Satisfaction|Get Satisfaction]] |accessdate=2008-07-29 |archive-date=2008-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080729013427/http://getsatisfaction.com/twitter/topics/twitter_im_down_may_23rd_may24th |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
